original_title: Heather Mabbott: I Didn't Mean to Say That
overview: Her quick wit and unique style has dazzled audiences all over the country.  Heather is a clean comedian and has performed with some of the best, like Caroline Rhea, Jimmy Walker, Bobcat Goldthwait, Bruce Baum, Sinbad, and many, many more.
title: Heather Mabbott: I Didn't Mean to Say That
